{"tid":1330980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想殺警犬嘅同我入嚟！","createTime":"2019-07-18T18:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T16:02:09.000Z","uid":82829,"like":395,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"f676688461bcb23ea1a3a241327fd006944c771c","tid":1330980,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:51:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千祈唔好。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我先直接講結論：香港社會嘅革命氣氛仲係太稀薄。打成點，係另一件事，唔好殺。<br />\n<br />\n先撇開道德唔講，齋講操作考慮。<br />\n<br />\n我都好想小栢林死全家，但現實係香港革命嘅氣候未成，武力潔癖嘅病人數目太多，你見毛ee忍唔住發TVB老脾，其實係反映緊佢地自己都好大爭扎。死一個差人嘅話，唔好話立法會班濕鳩議員肯定割蓆，連KOL（例如HOCC）都會唔敢出聲。然後<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國際社會見到嘅就係你班香港人散曬，冇得玩，冇水抽，外國勢力包括聯合國、歐盟、仲有美國果班左膠國會議員就會即時割蓆，人權法收皮。</span></strong>林鄭真係會一個屈尾十，成功番盤。<br />\n<br />\n咁撚辛苦先捱到今日有一絲希望，我唔要因為有兄弟忍唔住，錯手殺狗，而前功盡廢。<br />\n<br />\n殺左狗，唔係你一個人入去坐，係我地成個香港陪葬。落手前，三思。<br />\n<br />\n原po<br />\n<br />\n想殺警犬嘅同我入嚟！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1322490\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1322490</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"95ae96f411d244035b243a6fde2ca55856fce3c6","tid":1330980,"uid":5780,"like":192,"dislike":4,"score":188,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:54:00.000Z","msg":"唔明點解要殺<br />\n斷手斷腳會不會更好？"},{"pid":"9a958f48440769df8daf75b0a074148d7b71c555","tid":1330980,"uid":251414,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T18:54:29.000Z","msg":"721我地都要有好多（ 速龍小隊）， 係勝負嘅關鍵（just like Sha Tin Lee Sin）"},{"pid":"7540467f70ef61daa8f155916a4ccdca6b7f31ec","tid":1330980,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T19:34:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d06aa33d7871e25f2458749b4d788a3061593c5f","tid":1330980,"uid":6548,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T19:41:11.000Z","msg":"唔知驚咩浩園局 根本唔配入 入一堀一"},{"pid":"63e1628d50b2a14275185cccf0e4210ed85aaa4f","tid":1330980,"uid":105511,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T20:18:54.000Z","msg":"唔到我地控制"},{"pid":"957da60730092ac6475952fc65eb4c5fd6a24ba7","tid":1330980,"uid":268867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:43:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"126afd5dc0f44c4bf4c5ef1bdaa89a310fb86575","tid":1330980,"uid":128600,"like":19,"dislike":3,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T23:45:23.000Z","msg":"痴線咩，唔應該有任何人死~<br />\n要令差佬停止政治任務"},{"pid":"2bad2ca347cd0d32191e4b69fff2573968ae44c9","tid":1330980,"uid":32588,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:01:27.000Z","msg":"林鄭最想有差人死，認真<br />\n因為佢覺得形勢會逆轉<br />\n所以最多打佢一身就算<br />\n千祈唔好俾佢地有人死"},{"pid":"50a577c6b935f32d19f3c8532477544040845ff8","tid":1330980,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:08:05.000Z","msg":"<code>新聞po睇日期先覆，有人推舊po、出引戰po、傳聞po唔好覆，前面已經有人講咗「唔好覆」就唔好跟住留「唔好覆」否則你等同推po，一毛點摟屌你一覆就中計。俾正負評前睇埋最後一頁，唔好俾第一頁帶風向。721去遊行！</code>"},{"pid":"cfc50c1428d7a8ef9895fff5d919f1bb54875ffc","tid":1330980,"uid":171313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:09:44.000Z","msg":"9.5指算啦<br />\n留返佢哋條9命"},{"pid":"9e6390b641d3c73fb6a859053a648f6c29c355df","tid":1330980,"uid":230825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:10:49.000Z","msg":"push. 忍下手"},{"pid":"18086ba9056dde14babfb77983ced49f22cded73","tid":1330980,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T00:13:19.000Z","msg":"草船借箭：連儂見到720海報，唔使撕嘅，直接用marker將0改做1<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1331120\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1331120</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b7b91b23f2f6fbdb8fa9341533516ebda8d6e1b","tid":1330980,"uid":19176,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTim